amed “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance"}]},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio/contrastRatio(_:_:)":{"title":"contrastRatio(_:_:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/contrastRatio(_:_:)","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contrastRatio","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"Color","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI5ColorV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Color","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI5ColorV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Double","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"abstract":[{"text":"According to the  WCAG 2.1 algorithm, computes the contrat ratio between the current color and another","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"See https:\/\/www.w3.org\/WAI\/WCAG21\/Techniques\/general\/G18.html#procedure","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/contrastra